{% comment %}
  About Us Page — Dani Cleans
  Brand story, values, team info, and trust signals.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="about-page">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-container">
      <p class="about-tag">Our Story</p>
      <h1>About Dani Cleans</h1>
      <p class="about-hero-sub">Locally owned. Community driven. Committed to making Charlottesville homes and yards shine since 2018.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="about-story">
    <div class="about-container">
      <div class="about-story-grid">
        <div class="about-story-text">
          <h2>From One Home to Hundreds</h2>
          <p>Dani Cleans started with a simple idea: deliver cleaning and landscaping services that people can actually rely on. No missed appointments, no cutting corners, no hidden fees — just honest, thorough work by people who care.</p>
          <p>What began as a one-person operation in Charlottesville has grown into a trusted team serving hundreds of homes across the region. We added landscaping because our cleaning customers kept asking for it — and we realized that handling both indoor and outdoor care under one roof just makes life easier for everyone.</p>
          <p>Today, we serve Charlottesville, Albemarle County, Crozet, Waynesboro, Staunton, and surrounding communities. Every job still gets the same attention to detail that built our reputation from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-story-stats">
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num">500+</span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">Homes Served</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num">4.9</span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">Google Rating</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num">{{ 'now' | date: '%Y' | minus: 2018 }}+</span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">Years in Business</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="about-stat-num">98%</span>
            <span class="about-stat-label">Repeat Customers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="about-values">
    <div class="about-container">
      <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
      <div class="about-values-grid">
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2d6a4f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Trust & Reliability</h3>
          <p>Every team member is background-checked and trained. We show up on time, every time. Your home is safe in our hands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2d6a4f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Quality Over Shortcuts</h3>
          <p>We don't rush. We don't cut corners. Every surface, every blade of grass gets the attention it deserves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2d6a4f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Customer First</h3>
          <p>Your satisfaction isn't a goal — it's a guarantee. If something isn't right, we make it right. Period.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2d6a4f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Community Roots</h3>
          <p>We live here, we work here, and we give back here. Supporting local businesses and families is in our DNA.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2d6a4f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Eco-Conscious</h3>
          <p>We offer eco-friendly products and responsible disposal. Taking care of homes shouldn't mean hurting the environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2d6a4f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Team Growth</h3>
          <p>We invest in our people with training, fair wages, and growth opportunities. Happy teams do better work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Sets Us Apart -->
  <section class="about-difference">
    <div class="about-container">
      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <div class="about-diff-grid">
        <div class="about-diff-item">
          <div class="about-diff-num">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4>One Company, Complete Care</h4>
            <p>We handle both your home cleaning and landscaping. One company, one bill, one team that knows your property inside and out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-diff-item">
          <div class="about-diff-num">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Same Team Every Visit</h4>
            <p>No random crews. You get the same familiar, trained professionals who learn your home's specific needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-diff-item">
          <div class="about-diff-num">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4>No Contracts Ever</h4>
            <p>Month-to-month flexibility. Skip, pause, or cancel anytime. We earn your business every single visit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-diff-item">
          <div class="about-diff-num">4</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Iron-Clad Guarantee</h4>
            <p>Not satisfied? We come back and redo it free. Still not happy? We refund that visit. No questions asked.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Areas Served -->
  <section class="about-areas">
    <div class="about-container">
      <h2>Where We Work</h2>
      <p class="about-areas-sub">Proudly serving these communities across Central Virginia</p>
      <div class="about-area-tags">
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-charlottesville">Charlottesville</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-crozet">Crozet</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-waynesboro">Waynesboro</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-staunton">Staunton</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-keswick">Keswick</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-earlysville">Earlysville</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-scottsville">Scottsville</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-gordonsville">Gordonsville</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-palmyra">Palmyra</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-free-union">Free Union</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-ivy">Ivy</a>
        <a href="/pages/cleaning-services-in-north-garden">North Garden</a>
        <span class="about-area-more">Albemarle County</span>
        <span class="about-area-more">Nelson County</span>
        <span class="about-area-more">Augusta County</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="about-container">
      <h2>Ready to See the Difference?</h2>
      <p>Join hundreds of Charlottesville families who trust Dani Cleans with their home and property.</p>
      <div class="about-cta-buttons">
        <a href="/pages/request-a-quote" class="about-btn primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
        <a href="tel:4343510335" class="about-btn secondary">Call 434-351-0335</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  {% if page.content != blank %}
  <section class="about-extra">
    <div class="about-container">
      {{ page.content }}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<!-- Schema -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "LocalBusiness",
  "name": "Dani Cleans",
  "description": "Professional cleaning and landscaping services in Charlottesville, Virginia. Locally owned, fully insured.",
  "url": "{{ shop.url }}{{ page.url }}",
  "telephone": "+1-434-351-0335",
  "foundingDate": "2018",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Charlottesville",
    "addressRegion": "VA",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "areaServed": [
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Charlottesville" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Crozet" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Waynesboro" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Staunton" }
  ],
  "priceRange": "$$",
  "aggregateRating": {
    "@type": "AggregateRating",
    "ratingValue": "4.9",
    "reviewCount": "127"
  }
}
</script>

<style>
.about-page { color: #1a3a2a; }
.about-container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
.about-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a2a 0%, #2d6a4f 100%);
  color: #fff; padding: 80px 20px; text-align: center;
}
.about-tag {
  font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;
  opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.about-hero h1 { font-size: 44px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
.about-hero-sub { font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* Story */
.about-story { padding: 72px 20px; }
.about-story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; }
.about-story-text h2 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.about-story-text p { font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.about-story-stats {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px;
}
.about-stat {
  background: #f0f5f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 20px;
  text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e0e8e0;
}
.about-stat-num { display: block; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: #2d6a4f; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.about-stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: #666; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }

/* Values */
.about-values { padding: 72px 20px; background: #f7faf7; }
.about-values h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.about-values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
.about-value-card {
  background: #fff; padding: 32px 24px; border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid #e0e8e0; text-align: center;
}
.about-value-icon { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.about-value-card h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a3a2a; }
.about-value-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

/* Difference */
.about-difference { padding: 72px 20px; }
.about-difference h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.about-diff-grid { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
.about-diff-item {
  display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e8e0;
}
.about-diff-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.about-diff-num {
  width: 44px; height: 44px; min-width: 44px;
  background: #2d6a4f; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800;
}
.about-diff-item h4 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: #1a3a2a; }
.about-diff-item p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }

/* Areas */
.about-areas { padding: 56px 20px; background: #f7faf7; text-align: center; }
.about-areas h2 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.about-areas-sub { color: #666; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.about-area-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; }
.about-area-tags a {
  padding: 8px 18px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0e8e0;
  border-radius: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #2d6a4f; text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.about-area-tags a:hover { background: #2d6a4f; color: #fff; }
.about-area-more {
  padding: 8px 18px; background: transparent; border: 1px dashed #c0c8c0;
  border-radius: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #888;
}

/* CTA */
.about-cta {
  padding: 72px 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a2a, #2d6a4f);
  color: #fff; text-align: center;
}
.about-cta h2 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.about-cta p { font-size: 17px; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.about-cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.about-btn {
  padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.about-btn.primary { background: #fff; color: #2d6a4f; }
.about-btn.primary:hover { background: #f0f5f0; transform: translateY(-2px); }
.about-btn.secondary { border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color: #fff; }
.about-btn.secondary:hover { border-color: #fff; }

/* Extra content */
.about-extra { padding: 48px 20px; }
.about-extra h2, .about-extra h3 { color: #1a3a2a; }
.about-extra p { color: #555; line-height: 1.7; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-hero h1 { font-size: 30px; }
  .about-hero { padding: 56px 20px; }
  .about-story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-diff-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; align-items: center; }
}
</style>
